panels.title: Requests by Colo Code Over Time

queries.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*cloudflare*
| json field=_raw "ColoCode" 
| timeslice 15m 
| count by _timeslice, ColoCode 
| transpose row _timeslice column ColoCode

_sourceCategory=*cloudflare*
| json field=_raw "Email" 
| json field=_raw "SrcIP" 
| json field=_raw "DstIP" 
| where isValidIPv4(DstIP) 
| where isPublicIP(DstIP) 
| geoip DstIP 
| count latitude, longitude

_sourceCategory=*cloudflare*
| json field=_raw "Email" 
| json field=_raw "SrcIP" 
| json field=_raw "DstIP" 
| where isValidIPv4(SrcIP) 
| where isPublicIP(SrcIP) 
| geoip SrcIP 
| count latitude, longitude

_sourceCategory=*cloudflare*
| json field=_raw "ColoCode" 
| timeslice 15m 
| count by _timeslice 
| outlier _count direction=+

_sourceCategory=*cloudflare*
| json field=_raw "QueryName" 
| count by QueryName 
| top 10 QueryName by _count

_sourceCategory=cloudflare bytesreceived

| json field=_raw "BytesSent"
| json field=_raw "BytesReceived"
| timeslice 15m
| sum(BytesSent) as total_bytes_sent, sum(BytesReceived) as total_bytes_recevived by _timeslice

_sourceCategory=cloudflare 

| json field=_raw "Email"
| json field=_raw "DeviceName"
| json field=_raw "SourceIP"
| json field=_raw "OriginIP"
| json field=_raw "DeviceID"
| geoip OriginIP
| count latitude, longitude, Email, DeviceName

_sourceCategory=cloudflare Action

| json field=_raw "Email"
| json field=_raw "IPAddress"
| json field=_raw "Allowed"
| json field=_raw "Action"
| where Action="login" OR Action="logout"
| where Allowed = "true"
| geoip IPAddress
| count latitude, longitude, Email

_sourceCategory=cloudflare Action    

| json field=_raw "Email"
| json field=_raw "IPAddress"
| json field=_raw "Allowed"
| json field=_raw "Action"
| where Action="login"
| timeslice 15m
| count _timeslice
| outlier _count
//| transpose row _timeslice column action

_sourceCategory=cloudflare Action    

| json field=_raw "CreatedAt"
| json field=_raw "AppDomain"
| json field=_raw "Email"
| json field=_raw "IPAddress"
| json field=_raw "Allowed"
| json field=_raw "Action"
| where Action="login"
| where Allowed="false"
| count CreatedAt, Email, AppDomain

_sourceCategory=cloudflare Action

| json field=_raw "ActionResult"

| count by ResourceType

_sourceCategory=cloudflare Action

| json field=_raw "ActorType"
| json field=_raw "ActorEmail"

_sourceCategory=cloudflare Action

| json field=_raw "ResourceType"
| json field=_raw "ActionType"
| json field=_raw "ActorType"
| json field=_raw "ActorEmail"
| where ActionResult = "true"
| count

| json field=_raw "ActionResult"
